snippet.title: Hero: 108 Online Gameplay Trailer HD
snippet.description:
http://www.freemmogamer.com for all free to play MMORPGs and MMO Games.

Hero: 108 Online is a quirky fast-paced action multi-player online game (MMOG) featuring the same lively cartoon characters and storyline as its animated series counterpart, as well as the Hero: 108 collection of fun and innovative toys coming out this fall.
